---
---

<section
  class="bg-cream pt-24 pb-12 md:pt-32 md:pb-20 overflow-hidden relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center"
>
  <!-- Watermark Background Logo -->
  <div
    class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-[15%] pointer-events-none z-0"
  >
    <!-- SEO: Il tag alt descrittivo per l'immagine è oro -->
    <img
      src="/logo.webp"
      alt="Ti Aiuto con le Bollette - Consulente luce, gas e ottimizzazione energia per privati e partita IVA a Empoli e Toscana"
      class="w-[800px] md:w-[1200px] lg:w-[1300px] opacity-[0.08]"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Glow effect -->
  <div
    class="absolute right-1/4 top-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-orange/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 relative z-10 w-full">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Content -->
      <div class="py-6 md:py-20 text-balance">
        <div
          class="au inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-navy/5 text-navy text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-4 py-2 rounded-lg mb-8 border border-navy/10 relative"
        >
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange rounded-full"></span>
          Empoli e Provincia · Toscana
          <!-- Mossa da cecchino SEO -->
          <span class="sr-only"
            >Esperto consulente per analisi, risparmio e contestazione bollette
            luce gas Enel, Eni, mercato libero tutelato a empoli, firenze e provincia. Assistenza rincari fatture per
            attività e consumatori privati.</span
          >
        </div>
        <h1
          class="au1 text-4xl md:text-7xl font-black text-navy leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-8"
        >
          L'energia è una<br />questione di <span class="text-orange"
            >fiducia.</span
          >
        </h1>
        <p
          class="au2 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-md"
        >
          Più che un semplice cambio fornitore, una consulenza basata sulla
          <strong class="text-navy font-bold">stima professionale</strong> e sulla
          trasparenza totale. Ti aiutiamo a navigare nel mercato energetico con volti
          familiari.
        </p>
        <div class="au3 flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-10 md:mb-16">
          <a
            href="#contatti"
            class="bg-navy hover:bg-orange text-white font-black px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl text-sm uppercase tracking-widest transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-navy/20 hover:shadow-orange/20"
          >
            Inizia Ora
          </a>
          <a
            href="#servizi"
            class="bg-white border border-gray-100 text-navy hover:bg-gray-50 font-black px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl text-sm uppercase tracking-widest transition-all"
          >
            Scopri i Servizi
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Numeri di Fiducia -->
        <div
          class="au3 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-8 md:gap-10 pt-8 md:pt-10 border-t border-gray-100"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-navy">100%</div>
            <div
              class="text-[9px] text-orange font-black uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
            >
              Etico
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-navy">Diretto</div>
            <div
              class="text-[9px] text-orange font-black uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
            >
              Senza Call Center
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-navy">Locale</div>
            <div
              class="text-[9px] text-orange font-black uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
            >
              Vicino a Te
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Professional Trust Card -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex justify-end relative">
        <div class="relative group">
          <!-- Card principals -->
          <div
            class="bg-navy rounded-[40px] shadow-[0_32px_64px_-16px_rgba(0,18,51,0.5)] p-10 border border-white/5 w-[400px] relative z-10 transition-all duration-700 hover:-translate-y-2 group-hover:shadow-orange/10"
          >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
              Il valore del <span class="text-orange">rapporto</span> umano.
            </h3>

            <ul class="space-y-6 mb-10">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                  class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-orange/20 text-orange flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-current"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    ><path
                      d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/60 font-light leading-snug">
                  <strong class="text-white font-bold"
                    >Stima professionale:</strong
                  > Costruiamo un rapporto che dura nel tempo, non un semplice contratto.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                  class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-orange/20 text-orange flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-current"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    ><path
                      d="M13 3h-2v10h2V3zm4.83 2.17l-1.42 1.42C17.99 7.86 19 9.81 19 12c0 3.87-3.13 7-7 7s-7-3.13-7-7c0-2.19 1.01-4.14 2.58-5.42L6.17 5.17C4.23 6.82 3 9.26 3 12c0 4.97 4.03 9 9 9s9-4.03 9-9c0-2.74-1.23-5.18-3.17-6.83z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/60 font-light leading-snug">
                  <strong class="text-white font-bold">Zero Pressione:</strong> Ti
                  offriamo la nostra analisi, ma sei tu a decidere. Senza forzature.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                  class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-orange/20 text-orange flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-current"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    ><path
                      d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/60 font-light leading-snug">
                  <strong class="text-white font-bold"
                    >Ci mettiamo la faccia:</strong
                  > Restiamo i tuoi referenti diretti per qualsiasi dubbio o problema
                  futuro.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                <div
                  class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-navy bg-orange"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-navy bg-orange-light/40"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-navy bg-white/20"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest text-pretty"
              >
                Consulenza etica operante in Toscana
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative back elements -->
          <div
            class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-orange/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10 animate-pulse"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-navy/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Pulizia stili non necessari */
</style>
